Nautilus-ShareFtp
=================

Nautilus-ShareFtp

Download
--------

Download the [package][dlp] *or* checkout the source:

    $ git clone https://github.com/atareao/nautilus-shareftp.git

Installation
------------

    $ sudo add-apt-repositoy ppa:atareao/nautilus-extensions
    $ sudo apt-get update
    $ sudo apt-get install nautilus-shareftp
